Interface GTreeRootNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<GTreeNode>, GTreeNode, java.lang.Iterable<GTreeNode>
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractGTreeRootNode, DomainFolderRootNode, FSBRootNode, InProgressGTreeRootNode, NoProjectNode
    public interface GTreeRootNode
extends GTreeNode
    Root nodes must implement this interface. They only have one additional responsibility and that is they must support saving off the tree that they belong to.
